-What happened?
-We just drifted apart

08:04.700 --> 08:07.400
Oh, hey.What brings you here?

08:07.600 --> 08:11.000
-Bringing you lunch
-Well, what happened? A check bounce?

08:11.100 --> 08:16.400
No. Just felt like feeding my husband and,
you know,seeing how you're doing

08:16.500 --> 08:18.700
I'm fine. I think actually I figured it out

08:18.800 --> 08:20.100
-You did?
-Yeah

08:21.800 --> 08:27.200
My dad died this week 5 years ago.You know about this time
I always start to go into a kind of funk

08:27.300 --> 08:33.200
The only difference is this year I forgot.So maybe it's just been
weighing on me, and I didn't even notice it

08:33.299 --> 08:37.299
-Huh. Ok, so you're feeling better now?
-Yeah, absolutely

08:37.400 --> 08:41.200
-You sure then?
-Yeah.You worry too much

08:41.600 --> 08:44.000
I worry just enough. I'm going to work

08:44.100 --> 08:47.400
-Love you
-Mmm. Love you back

